{"tid":2399768,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[估國家] 華裔少年走上高速公路 企圖尋短遭警槍殺！家屬提告","createTime":"2021-02-08T11:42:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T12:59:15.000Z","uid":17387,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9bdbebb02643f5995da977ff3d1df8acd151c10b","tid":2399768,"uid":17387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:42:07.000Z","msg":"美國一名華裔少年去年底因走在高速公路上企圖尋短，警方到場時，少年一度拿槍指警察，警方對他開槍喪命。日前少年家屬主張當時死者「尋求協助」，但反遭警殺害，因此委託律師向法院提起訴訟，控告涉事警察。<br />\n<br />\n微博「頭條新聞」指出，美國賓夕法尼亞州一名少年去年12月30疑似抑鬱症發作，走上高速公路意圖輕生，警方接獲通報到場。本月4日律師曝光案發當時影片表示，該名少年雖一度舉槍，但隨後雙手求饒，卻響起槍聲遭警方擊斃。律師說，警方說法與目擊者提出影片似乎有出入。<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/6oaKMHPu3kb4q_Cjpq7hZlqmX7w=/310x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ADVHM56W6BDAVKXKFJU4BD6MVA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F6oaKMHPu3kb4q_Cjpq7hZlqmX7w%3D%2F310x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FADVHM56W6BDAVKXKFJU4BD6MVA.png&h=cee75cee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n死者家屬委由律師指出，現場看來該少年當時考慮自殺，他在大聲呼救，之後舉起雙手仍遭警方開槍，身體中彈。涉案警察曾停職接受調查，但目前已重返工作崗位。死者少年家屬請求當局展開調查，也打算提起民事訴訟。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210208/VXHGOAOQVVF5FBINYCICFQ4VTI/?utm_campaign=twad_social_appledaily.tw&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=photo_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR37OohoJPsJmuU0Qplo86sJgcKZMG08vb4CX2jHDEZUGr-xG_78xScdsqE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210208%2FVXHGOAOQVVF5FBINYCICFQ4VTI%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_appledaily.tw%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dphoto_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR37OohoJPsJmuU0Qplo86sJgcKZMG08vb4CX2jHDEZUGr-xG_78xScdsqE&d=wuzGI5SyrIdJ%2FUQuqXTUiuF5TOcUp1XGW39uuIwQJ%2Fg%3D&h=dc7eccba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%